1. ppa-apraxia-analysis-code.R contains R script for Dresang, Williamson, Kim, Hillis, & Buxbaum analysis.
2. ppa-apraxia-supplemental-materials.pdf contains the supplemental materials for Dresang, Williamson, Kim, Hillis, & Buxbaum manuscript.
3. gesture-items.txt includes pantomimed gestures used for this experiment (Buxbaum et al., 2014 for additional details).
4. gesture-procedure.txt explains details of the gesture imitation experiment task and coding protocol.
Please contact the authors for additional information.
